      %li Opt-out of allowing Civic Labs to collect your geographic location by changing the location settings on your mobile device
      %li Opt-out of linking your activity on the Site to your social networking sites, such as Facebook, Twitter, and Google Plus
      %li De-activate your profile (but your comments will still remain on the Site)
